1. *Naročito* se trudim da napravim dobro delo. (I especially strive to do a good deed.)
2. On je bio *naročito* zainteresovan za tu temu. (He was particularly interested in this topic.)
3. *Naročitom* pažnjom pratim njegove aktivnosti. (I follow his activities with particular attention.)
4. *Naročito* se osećam usamljeno tokom večeri. (I feel especially lonely during the evenings.)
5. *Naročito* se trudim da ispunim roditeljske zahteve. (I especially strive to fulfill parental requirements.)